Fort Hamilton Presb. Church
94th St. & 4th Ave.
Rev. Montgomery Mann
Entire building renovated, inside & outside. Outside work included painting of building, patching cement work, building new concrete wall in front, around lawn and new fence in rear, making new window sceeens, and leveling and seeding grass plot.
